data.description:
Wonderful home with so many great features! Assumable loan: 2.25%!
This spacious home has a bright, open feel! The kitchen features lovely updates, including a backsplash and updated countertops.  The dining room opens onto the spacious deck, perfect for entertaining or just relaxing! Gleaming hardwood floors throughout. The lower level bedroom features beautiful flooring and a spacious third bedroom! The level backyard is perfect for all of your outdoor activities! In a great location, close to amenities! Don't miss the chance to make this great home yours!
